Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,First impressions matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They matter because they could
