Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then instead, start things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,off with a great first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now suppose you're planning a
