Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're met with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now does this look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone wants you to register
