Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now consider this military base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,with its fortified exterior.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The message to anyone on the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,outside is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Compare that to Apple Union
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Square in San Francisco.
