Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,passersby to wonder in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And wondering is exactly what
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they do because people use -- as
