Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for a test drive or try on an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All without obstacles or
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,friction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first launch experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,should feel just as
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,frictionless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If people are greeted with an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,open, interactive experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the very first time they tap
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,your icon, you're going to make
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a great first impression and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,keep them coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's talk about some ways to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:02:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be discussing some tips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for leading with content first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How to teach new users about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,your app through interaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you need to ask for
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,some more information upfront,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,some tips on timing that will
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,add to a great user experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's start with some
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,strategies with a content first
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's compare our travel app to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,another travel app.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is Jetsetter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And the very first time you open
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jetsetter you're immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,greeted with this great content.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Big beautiful images.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Useful information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can browse this feed, of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,course, or you can jump right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,into search if you have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,something specific in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If a destination catches your
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,attention, you can drill in for
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,more photos and more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been seconds since you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,first launched this app and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you're already using it like a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're intrigued by all this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,great content and you've already
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,started daydreaming about laying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,on this beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only when you're ready to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,book the trip that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,prompted to register.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,By now, you've got a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of what the app has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen the potential
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,benefits of registering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So this feels like a more
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,appropriate time to share more
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,details.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not convinced yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,just compare Jetsetter with our
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,other travel app.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we've all been through some
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,version of that top row.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of these feels more
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,welcoming to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Always lead with great content.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Show off what makes your app
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,great right off the bat and let
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,people dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there are some situations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,where a little bit of upfront
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,instruction might be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say might because before
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you start incorporating some of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the tips we're about to look at,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to very carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,consider whether any upfront
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,instruction is needed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a quick look at the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,phone app.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now just imagine if we designed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,this with a series of first run
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,tool tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a little ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This interface is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We know how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You should strive to design your
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,interfaces to be as intuitive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and as easy to understand as
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ideally no upfront instruction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is needed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at Lara Croft
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,GO.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your starting point
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No onboarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to pull your attention
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,from this immersive experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right in the game but you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,still need to learn how to play
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So these first two levels are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,designed to introduce you to the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you only have a straight
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,line here and Lara looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,she's ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since there are no visible
