Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And sure enough, she starts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,moving in the direction you've
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,gestured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You quickly discover you can
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,move up and down walls too.
