Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've got this glowing tile
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,up ahead catching your
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,attention.
