Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,let's go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you've just completed a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,level.
