Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,playing the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Level 2 starts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like your path is cut
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,short.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's try that switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah ha, the missing path fills in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've figured out another
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,important part about how this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,game works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, of course, things get
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot more complex from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can start to see how
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,instruction can be layered into
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And again, no onboarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No tool tips or floating hands
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no barriers when you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,first play Lara Croft GO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This approach works in all kinds
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of apps not just games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Streaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a simple app designed to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,help you pick up new habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In my case as you might be able
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to guess I'm studying French and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to make a habit of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,practicing every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Streaks can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The completion of a task is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,represented by the filling in of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first launch experience
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,conveys this in a clever way by
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,inviting you to fill in rings as
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you proceed through this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're led right into
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,creating your first habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So if your app requires a bit of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,upfront education, it's going to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,be a lot more compelling if it's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,interactive and gives people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that sense of jumping right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach through interactive
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now another place you don't want
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,people to get stuck is with
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,permission requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know what it's like to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,open an app for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and get hit with permission
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,request after permission
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of like that demanding
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,landlord we met earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's look at some tips for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,getting this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Strava.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Strava lets you use your iPhone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to track outdoor runs and bike
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,rides.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it eventually asks for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,access to your location, your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,camera, your context, even
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,HealthKit data but it doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,ask for all of these right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, Strava makes requests
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,on an as needed basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, it's not until
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you're ready to take Strava out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for a ride for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're prompted to share
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,your location.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So you hit record down on the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get you on a ride here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's ready to roll?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get on ride and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually a little while later,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you're ready to wrap things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make it a short ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So you stop the ride and you tap
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,save.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now when you're saving a ride,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you have the option to add more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,details including a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only when you tap add a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,photo that you're prompted for
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,access to your photo library.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is another great
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,example of a permission request
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that's right in context.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So you immediately see the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,benefit and no additional
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,explanation is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's the same situation when
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for friends on Strava in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,your contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The app requests permissions on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a need to know basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you retain a sense of control
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,over both the experience and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,your private data.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there are a few apps out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,there that can't offer any value
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,without some sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,permissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Transit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It lists departures of nearby
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,buses and trains ordered based
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,on proximity to your current
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I live in San Francisco and I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,use this one all the time to get
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it wouldn't be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,provide this data without your
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first time you launch the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,app, you are prompted to share
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,your location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And as soon as you tap allow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the map zooms in and you're
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,presented with a list of nearby
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,routes and departure times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So you immediately see the value
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Transit will provide in exchange
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,for this information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So remember, ensure people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,understand the value of sharing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,their private data with you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ideally before you ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Once that permission has been
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,granted, reinforce the decision
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,by showing off the benefits
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll provide with that data.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Only ask for what's needed when
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it's needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow these tips and I promise
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll make a great first
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
